              "subtype": "change",
              "text": "- Swap out the herexen's weapon for the deity's favored weapon. If the weapon is simple, increase the damage die by one step; if it's two-handed, decrease the herexen's attack bonus with that weapon by 2.",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            {
